---
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro';
import Container from '@/components/Container.astro';
---
<Layout title="About - Rucking Revolution" description="Our mission, philosophy, the movement, and contact information" currentPage="/about">
  <Container>
    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Rucking Revolution</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted">
        Building a movement through discipline, leadership, and field readiness
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted mb-6">
        Rucking Revolution exists to professionalize rucking as a discipline and make it accessible to anyone ready to carry the load. We believe that weighted walking is more than exercise—it's a practice that builds physical resilience, mental toughness, and community bonds.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted">
        We provide structured knowledge, training programs, and leadership resources that help individuals and crews develop the skills, doctrine, and culture needed for rucking as a lifelong pursuit.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Discipline First</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Rucking rewards consistency over intensity. We emphasize progressive overload, proper form, and sustainable training habits that build resilience over time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Leadership in Motion</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Every ruck is an opportunity to lead and be led. Our platform teaches leadership principles through crew dynamics, after-action reviews, and field exercises.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Community Sustains</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Individual ruckers are strong. Rucking crews are unstoppable. We build tools and resources that help crews form, grow, and sustain their practice together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Movement</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted mb-6">
        Rucking Revolution is more than a website—it's a growing network of individuals, crews, and communities who share a commitment to carrying the load together. From weekend warriors to professional ruckers, our platform serves everyone who answers the call of the weighted march.
      </p>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">For Individuals</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted space-y-2">
            <li>Training programs and workout generators</li>
            <li>Performance kit guides and recommendations</li>
            <li>Route planning and event discovery</li>
            <li>Leadership development resources</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">For Crews</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted space-y-2">
            <li>Crew formation and culture building</li>
            <li>After-action review systems</li>
            <li>Team training programming</li>
            <li>Event coordination tools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="/learn" class="block p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Knowledge Base</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            In-depth articles, guides, and digital resources covering rucking theory, training methodology, and leadership principles.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/train" class="block p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Training Programs</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Structured workout generators, performance kit guides, and progressive training programs for all skill levels.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/lead" class="block p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Leadership & Crews</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Resources for building and leading rucking crews, including crew tactics, after-action reviews, and club development.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Join the Revolution</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted mb-6">
        Whether you're carrying your first ruck or leading a crew of hundreds, there's a place for you in the Rucking Revolution.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/learn/articles" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
          Start Learning
        </a>
        <a href="/train" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 border border-primary text-primary font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          Begin Training
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>
</Layout>
